<P>It is with great sorrow that I must announce that 
my beloved father, Phil Danzig died of cancer at 8:30 pm on October 27, 2004.
</p> 

<P>My personal home page :<a href="http://www.danzig.us/personal/"> www.danzig.us/personal</a>.</p>
